metadata.name: Your Totenkopf logo looks too similar to our BAYC
metadata.description: This is to commemorate RRBAYC's 5th take down. This time it wasn't DMCA'd - It was a trademark move because apparently the totenkopf logo ryder used is crossing trademark boundaries by looking just like the BAYC ape. This will forever be in art history as a self own.
